{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "菲约尔姆 第3话 炎之侵略",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "放火！\\n把所有叛徒统统烧死！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "住手！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "村子在燃烧……\\n太残酷了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "“叛变的王子”！\\n又来碍事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "为什么要做出如此残暴的事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "胆敢反抗伟大的狄涅尔帝国的家伙，\\n必须给予惩罚才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "所以就要像这样，\\n净化整个村子才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "这种惨无人道的单方面暴力，\\n竟还大言不惭地说是净化。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "那还用说。这正是我们\\n“黑暗火炬”被赋予的使命！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "什么！？说到黑暗火炬，\\n不就是那个随随便便就放火烧村、\\n臭名昭著的部队吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "什么净化……什么使命！\\n你们只是在四处破坏……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "不可原谅！\\n呀啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "蠢货，没头没脑的突击对我们没用！\\n迎击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "不能原谅！绝对不能原谅！\\n哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂！菲约尔姆！？\\n尤蒂尔，我们追！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯。放任她一个人\\n实在太危险了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120081_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "队长",
            "context": "给我通通烧光！\\n1只老鼠也不准放过！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "呃……火势越来越大……\\n无法接近敌人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "菲约尔姆公主，暂且撤退吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "火势越来越大，这样下去得不偿失。\\n先让村民们避难吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "好吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "兰扎卜，埃尔菲莉丝，\\n麻烦你们疏导村民！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好！一定会让所有人\\n都平安逃到村外的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n菲约尔姆公主就拜托你了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "菲约尔姆公主，\\n我们也该……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "那、那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "公主！你要去哪！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "啊啊……啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "没能逃掉吗。\\n你真不走运啊，小鬼！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "救命啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "不好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "呜……我才不会\\n输给你们这些家伙！哈啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵",
            "context": "呃啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……哈啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "菲约尔姆公主！\\n你这伤……得尽快治疗才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "这点小伤……没事的……\\n小朋友，你快逃吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "可是，你的伤都怪我……\\n不疼吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "我没事……\\n快躲到安全的地方去……好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "少年",
            "context": "我、我知道了……\\n对不起，大姐姐……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "菲约尔姆公主！\\n好严重的烧伤……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n我们先到安全的地方去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好。来，菲约尔姆公主，\\n抓住我的肩膀。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "非常抱歉……\\n呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（今天的菲约尔姆公主……\\n和平时简直判若两人。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（到底发生了什么……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110328_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "菲约尔姆",
            "context": "母亲……我，我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_KNIGHTSSTORY_110328_01_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}